desc: This Afternoon: Mostly cloudy, then gradually becoming sunny, with a high near 67. Breezy, with a west wind 16 to 18 mph, with gusts as high as 31 mph.
Tonight: Mostly clear, with a low around 40. West wind 6 to 11 mph becoming light northwest  after midnight. Winds could gust as high as 20 mph.
Friday: Scattered showers after 3pm.  Partly sunny, with a high near 58. East southeast wind 6 to 10 mph.  Chance of precipitation is 30%.
Friday Night: Scattered showers.  Cloudy, with a low around 46. East wind around 10 mph, with gusts as high as 18 mph.  Chance of precipitation is 50%.

Saturday: Scattered showers before 9am.  Mostly cloudy, then gradually becoming sunny, with a high near 80. Southeast wind 8 to 13 mph becoming south southwest in the afternoon. Winds could gust as high as 22 mph.  Chance of precipitation is 40%.
Saturday Night: Partly cloudy, with a low around 61.
Sunday: Scattered showers after 3pm.  Mostly sunny, with a high near 80. Breezy.  Chance of precipitation is 40%.
Sunday Night: Showers likely, mainly after 9pm.  Mostly cloudy, with a low around 53.
Monday: Showers likely, mainly before 9am.  Mostly cloudy, with a high near 62.
